{"segment":9,"line_start":440,"line_end":490,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_li_ma_hu","speaker_name":"李马虎","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"花生豆干全都免费，酒也请尽量喝，马马虎虎算了。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":17,"line_start":444,"line_end":444},{"speaker":"char_li_ma_hu","speaker_name":"李马虎","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"大爷你嫌这酒不好？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":17,"line_start":450,"line_end":452},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_li_ma_hu","text":"\"酒很好。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":17,"line_start":454,"line_end":454},{"speaker":"char_li_ma_hu","speaker_name":"李马虎","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"就算不好，也该马马虎虎喝两杯，散散心。\"","tone":"温柔","chapter":17,"line_start":456,"line_end":456},{"speaker":"char_li_ma_hu","speaker_name":"李马虎","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"凭良心讲，我也常常觉得奇怪，我怎么会开杂货铺？\"","tone":"苦笑","chapter":17,"line_start":466,"line_end":468},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_li_ma_hu","text":"\"你不喜欢喝酒？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":17,"line_start":470,"line_end":470},{"speaker":"char_li_ma_hu","speaker_name":"李马虎","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"根本不会喝，现在我已经快醉了。\"","tone":"无奈","chapter":17,"line_start":472,"line_end":472},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_li_ma_hu","text":"\"不会喝为什么要喝？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":17,"line_start":476,"line_end":476},{"speaker":"char_li_ma_hu","speaker_name":"李马虎","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"酒若温好，不喝就会坏的。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":17,"line_start":478,"line_end":478},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_li_ma_hu","text":"\"所以你宁可喝醉。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":17,"line_start":482,"line_end":482},{"speaker":"char_li_ma_hu","speaker_name":"李马虎","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"无论谁要开杂货铺，都得先学会一件事。\"","tone":"无奈","chapter":17,"line_start":486,"line_end":486},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_li_ma_hu","text":"\"什么事？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":17,"line_start":488,"line_end":488},{"speaker":"char_li_ma_hu","speaker_name":"李马虎","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"宁可自己受点罪，也绝不能糟塌一点东西。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":17,"line_start":490,"line_end":490}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":10,"line_start":492,"line_end":540,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_li_ma_hu","speaker_name":"李马虎","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"所以只有最没出息的人，才会开杂货铺，开杂货铺的人非但娶不到老婆，连朋友都没有一个。\"","tone":"苦笑","chapter":17,"line_start":492,"line_end":494},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_li_ma_hu","text":"\"你错了。\"","tone":"无奈","chapter":17,"line_start":496,"line_end":496},{"speaker":"char_li_ma_hu","speaker_name":"李马虎","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"我哪点错了？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":17,"line_start":498,"line_end":498},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_li_ma_hu","text":"\"世上只有一种人是真正没有朋友的。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":17,"line_start":500,"line_end":500},{"speaker":"char_li_ma_hu","speaker_name":"李马虎","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"哪种人？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":17,"line_start":502,"line_end":502},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_li_ma_hu","text":"\"我这种。\"","tone":"悲伤","chapter":17,"line_start":504,"line_end":504},{"speaker":"char_li_ma_hu","speaker_name":"李马虎","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"那位叶公子不是你的朋友？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":17,"line_start":514,"line_end":516},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_li_ma_hu","text":"\"不是。\"","tone":"冷酷","chapter":17,"line_start":518,"line_end":518},{"speaker":"char_li_ma_hu","speaker_name":"李马虎","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"但他却好像已将你当做朋友。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":17,"line_start":520,"line_end":520},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_li_ma_hu","text":"\"那只因为他有毛病。\"","tone":"冷酷","chapter":17,"line_start":522,"line_end":522},{"speaker":"char_li_ma_hu","speaker_name":"李马虎","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"有毛病？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":17,"line_start":524,"line_end":524},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_li_ma_hu","text":"\"拿我当朋友的人，都有毛病。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":17,"line_start":526,"line_end":526},{"speaker":"char_li_ma_hu","speaker_name":"李马虎","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"这么看来，我好像也有点毛病的了。\"","tone":"苦笑","chapter":17,"line_start":528,"line_end":528},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_li_ma_hu","text":"\"你？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":17,"line_start":530,"line_end":530},{"speaker":"char_li_ma_hu","speaker_name":"李马虎","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"因为我现在也很想交你这个朋友。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":17,"line_start":532,"line_end":532},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_li_ma_hu","text":"\"你这饭炒得并不好。\"","tone":"冷酷","chapter":17,"line_start":536,"line_end":536}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":11,"line_start":542,"line_end":548,"dialogues":[],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_li_ma_hu","updates":{"one_line":"李马虎伸手想拍傅红雪肩头时，手背突然被刀钉住。","source_refs":[{"chapter":17,"line_start":542,"line_end":548,"text":"他的肩已后缩，显见得心里很不平静。李马虎眼睛里突然露出种很奇怪的表情，慢慢地伸出手，好像要去拍他的肩。就在这时，突然间寒光一闪！一柄刀已钉入了他的手背。"}]},"relationship_updates":[]}]}
